title Dynamic View: Task Management - Task Service\nLuồng lấy danh sách Column kèm List Task

participant <<Container>>\nAPI Gateway as API Gateway
participant <<Component>>\nSecurity Filter Chain as Security Filter Chain
participant <<Component>>\nController as Controller
participant <<Component>>\nService as Service
participant <<Component>>\nRepository as Repository
participant <<Container>>\nTask DB as Task DB

API Gateway->Security Filter Chain: 1. GET /api/projects/{id}/columns
Security Filter Chain->Controller: 2. Forward request
Controller->Service: 3. getColumnsWithTasks(projectId)
Service->Repository: 4. Query joined data
Repository->Task DB: 5. SELECT columns, tasks...
